        generate methods (with bodies) corresponding to given method declaration there are maybe two method implementations for one declaration (e.g. EJB' create() -> ejbCreate(), ejbPostCreate() )
        Parameters:
        aClass - context for method implementations
        method - method to override or implement
        toCopyJavaDoc - true if copy JavaDoc from method declaration
        Returns:
        list of method prototypes
